{"tid":1200751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懲教署職員疑欠債 赤柱宿舍燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-06-10T22:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T02:24:58.000Z","uid":41404,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7589d60b5ac194b66d31efc9598328c774860840","tid":1200751,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:32:02.000Z","msg":"赤柱東頭灣里懲教署職員宿舍，昨晚10時許，一名48歲姓梁女子報案，指其50歲姓李丈夫反鎖在流手間內，疑燒炭自殺。救援人員到場爆門後，發現事主倒卧浴缸，旁邊有一盤燒過的炭，他當場證實死亡。警方撿獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n據知事主為懲教署職員，疑因欠債輕生。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=c284163f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190611/59700580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F59700580&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=bd6e7419\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F59700580&h=e3bd579f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190611/59700580</a>"},{"pid":"2f3b6559a4104881601b8abd0d168f3e7befb291","tid":1200751,"uid":52122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:33:27.000Z","msg":"廢物"},{"pid":"bdd5b1fa48a91732ad01cf456562d38e67b3a279","tid":1200751,"uid":113626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賭仔, 無論社會經濟幾好你都唔會係受惠者"},{"pid":"2bf831c0ba5281e98f6be9c5c5